targets.query: SELECT "value" AS "application" FROM "softwareVersion" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT "serverInfo" AS "Version" FROM "tomcat_Server" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter
SELECT (mean("Percent_Processor_Time")/$ncpu) FROM "win_process" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "instance" =~ /^tomcat/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("Private_Bytes") FROM "win_process" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "instance" =~ /^tomcat/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("Working_Set_-_Private") FROM "win_process" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "instance" =~ /^tomcat/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("IO_Read_Bytes_persec") FROM "win_process" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "instance" =~ /^tomcat/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("IO_Write_Bytes_persec") FROM "win_process" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "instance" =~ /^tomcat/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT mean("Handle_Count") FROM "win_process" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "instance" =~ /^tomcat/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("HeapMemoryUsage.max") AS "Heap Size Limit", mean("HeapMemoryUsage.used") AS "Heap Used", mean("HeapMemoryUsage.committed") AS "Heap Committed", mean("NonHeapMemoryUsage.used") AS "NonHeap Used", mean("NonHeapMemoryUsage.committed") AS "NonHeap Committed" FROM "tomcat_jvm_memory" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)

SELECT mean("DaemonThreadCount") AS "Daemon Count", mean("PeakThreadCount") AS "Peak Count", mean("ThreadCount") AS "Count" FROM "CMS_java-lang_Threading" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval)

SELECT difference("bytesReceived") AS "Bytes Received", difference("bytesSent") AS "Bytes Sent" FROM "tomcat_GlobalRequestProcessor" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tomcat_connector$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"

SELECT difference("requestCount") AS "Request Count", difference("errorCount") AS "Error Count" FROM "tomcat_GlobalRequestProcessor" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tomcat_connector$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT difference("processingTime") AS "Processing Time" FROM "tomcat_GlobalRequestProcessor" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tomcat_connector$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"

SELECT "maxThreads" AS "Max Threads", "currentThreadCount" AS "Current Threads", "currentThreadsBusy" AS "Current Threads Busy" FROM "tomcat_ThreadPool" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tomcat_connector$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT "connectionCount" AS "Connections" FROM "tomcat_ThreadPool" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/ AND "name" =~ /^$Tomcat_connector$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT difference("CollectionCount") FROM "tomcat_jvm_garbage_collector" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"
SELECT difference("CollectionTime") FROM "tomcat_jvm_garbage_collector" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "name"

SELECT mean("CollectionUsage.committed") AS "Commited", mean("CollectionUsage.init") AS "Init", mean("CollectionUsage.max") AS "Max", mean("PeakUsage.used") AS "Used" FROM "tomcat_jvm_memory_pool" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(none)

SELECT mean("PeakUsage.committed") AS "Commited", mean("PeakUsage.init") AS "Init", mean("CollectionUsage.max") AS "Max", mean("PeakUsage.used") AS "Used" FROM "tomcat_jvm_memory_pool" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(none)

SELECT mean("Usage.committed") AS "Commited", mean("Usage.init") AS "Init", mean("Usage.max") AS "Max", mean("Usage.max") AS "Used" FROM "tomcat_jvm_memory_pool" WHERE ("host" =~ /^$server$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(none)
SELECT mean("Percent_Processor_Time") FROM "win_cpu" WHERE "host" = 'itrivsuswp01' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time($interval) fill(null)
